GREENLAND-WEST COAST.
VESSEL, TWO PERSONS ON BOARD, DISABLED AND ADRIFT
DUE TO ENGINE DAMAGE VICINITY OF TRACKLINE
BETWEEN ILULISSAT (69-13N 051-06W) AND
NIAQORNAARSUK (68-13N 052-51W). VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
REPORTS TO AASIAAT RADIO.
